"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-michael-phelps-reacts-leon-marchands-historic-olympic-double-gold-paris-21338421\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Michael Phelps claims Leon Marchand delivered 'the greatest double in the history of the sport' after the Frenchman won twoOlympicgold medals inParison Wednesday night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.960318430962653e-49, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In front of 17,000 fans in La Defense Arena, Marchand was cheered on by a loud contingent of French supporters as he kicked off his evening by beating the reigning champion and world-record holder, Hungary's Kristof Milak, in the 200m butterfly.\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.7979066945535501, \"rank\": 0.1280259568899423, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9990117754864338, \"rank\": 0.0009891268577028863, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"score\": 0.9548182616217314, \"rank\": 0.04731958261869196, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than two hours after winning his first gold, Marchand returned for his second event of the evening and delivered a commanding performance to win the 200m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999951041196959, \"rank\": 4.800687149012213e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old Frenchman, who made his Olympic debut in Paris three years ago but did not win a medal, is the first swimmer to win two golds in one evening in 48 years after EastGermany's Kornelia Ender achieved the same feat in 1976.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999806505, \"rank\": 1.9356330461453675e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kornelia_Ender\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kornelia Ender\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kornelia_Ender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kornelia_Ender\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps, meanwhile, remains the most-decorated Olympian of all time with 28 medals from his career in the pool and the 39-year-old American still holds the record for the most golds, 23, in the history of the Games.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4703062206217024e-12, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998014433943732, \"rank\": 0.00013743929239992363, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think the easiest thing for me is that's probably the greatest double I have seen in the history of the sport,' Phelps said of Marchand's achievement on NBC's Olympic coverage.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999689669044, \"rank\": 3.103084231062935e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999951041196959, \"rank\": 4.800687149012213e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6483573544531186, \"rank\": 0.3348641734517249, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To be able to go 1.52 and 2.05\\u2026 the kid can obviously swim.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We know that and if we did not know it before, he's going to be here a long time and he's going to make a lot of noise.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The voice, the cheer, everything there, the electricity.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait to talk to him to hear what it felt like.'\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps was also blown away by the performance of China's Pan Zhanle, who smashed his own\\u00a0100m freestyle\\u00a0world record after Marchand completed his double on Wednesday evening.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999689669044, \"rank\": 3.103084231062935e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9524668448511243, \"rank\": 0.04492092179654726, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999951041196959, \"rank\": 4.800687149012213e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 19-year-old registered a blistering time of of 46.40, lowering his previous record by a full four tenths of a second, while Australia's Kyle Chalmers won silver and Romania's David Popovici took Bronze.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyle Chalmers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.882924420182878, \"rank\": 0.13256572982009285, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Popovici\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Winning the 100m free by over a second\\u2026 holy crap, that is mind-blowing for me,' Phelps said of Pan's new record.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 1998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999689669044, \"rank\": 3.103084231062935e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have never seen a win of that margin in that race I do not think in my career.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To go 46.4, that's unheard of.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be that much closer to going 45 seconds in a long course 100m freestyle, I can not understand that, I really can not.'\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Rafael Nadal shares retirement update after Olympic dream comes to brutal end  ArrowMORE:Olympic duo in nasty fall-out with best player in the world branded 'insincere'  ArrowMORE:Olympic venue evacuated after severe weather warning in Paris  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999806505, \"rank\": 1.9356330461453675e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 3055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  Th